channel.title: PrecisionX - Renovating rsps - Make it or break it
channel.description:
[center]Hi and welcome to Precision X
We are a Brand new , pre - eoc , economy based server! We aim to provide the best possible service for anyone that wishes to join! It is a challenging eco with lots of new content , including fully working dwarf cannons , and custom systems to make the community happy!
As a note , we like critisism , we do not take offence , instead we resolve the problems and aim to make Precision X better for the players. We like to think that our server , one day could reach a very great amount of players. But we need your help with this!
Come and join Precision X today at Precision X
There are pictures attached to the post on what we have to offer
We hope to see you soon
-PrecisionX[/center]
